 It looked more like a costume than clothing, and Jakub wondered if she
 was promoting a play.
 He glanced at his wristwatch… he had a little time before he needed to
 get home.
 Curious, he paused and glanced both ways along the street, then crossed.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
