\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
“Jdi dovnitř a čekej na další pokyny.
 Jdeme do války,” the woman said, and Jakub found himself nodding and agreeing,
 since of course he had already intended to go inside and wait quietly for
 further instruction.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
He pushed open the door to the theatre.
